dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Avenal Gap quadrangle, Kings and Kern Counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Avenal Gap, CA 1954, Photorevised 1973, AMS 2055 IV SW - Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
